ank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20as%20of%20Monday%2C%20one%20of%20the%20suspects%20%E2%80%94%20the%20niece%20of%20a%20man%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%20%E2%80%94%20still%20hadn't%20been%20apprehended.%20It%20said%20that%20on%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20incident%20in%20Rincon%2C%20she%20committed%20%26quot%3Bsimilar%20theft%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20Walmart%20near%20Savannah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHansbrough%20%26quot%3Bwas%20fired%20for%20attempting%20to%20stop%20the%20theft%26quot%3B%20because%20her%20action%20of%20grabbing%20the%20cart%20violated%20company%20policy%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20Many%20retailers%20have%20strict%20policies%20that%20prohibit%20staff%20from%20stopping%20shoplifters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20say%20that%20if%20you%20see%20somebody%20stealing%20something%20out%20the%20door%2C%20not%20to%20pursue%2C%20not%20to%20go%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Hansbrough%20told%20local%20news%20outlet%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.effinghamherald.net%2Flocal%2Fhealing-and-moving-forward-former-lowes-employee-looking-new-job%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Effingham%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20lost%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20expect%20to%20get%20terminated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20a%20reprimand%20or%20a%20suspension.%26quot%3B%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fdonna-hansbrough-after-being-wrongfully-fired%3Futm_campaign%3Dp_cp%2Bshare-sheet%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26fbclid%3DIwAR3cubD58nN286mZ7JHOsE7Jck9CVyFGGeDV2jwtzsWuXcpQlEmK5nx0ApU%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efundraiser%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20up%20for%20Hansbrough%20raised%20more%20than%20%2425%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELowe's%20confirmed%20to%20The%20Herald%20on%20Monday%20that%20Hansbrough%20had%20been%20given%20her%20job%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20senior%20management%20became%20