80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2015%2C%202019%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20announced%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20which%20promised%20tap%20water%20supply%20provisions%20to%20every%20rural%20household%20by%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20written%20reply%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2024%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Jal%20Shakti%20said%20that%20so%20far%20according%20to%20data%20provided%20by%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%2C%20out%20of%2019.46%20crore%20rural%20households%20in%20the%20country%2C%20approximately%2012.57%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20or%2064.61%25%20%E2%80%93%20households%20are%20reported%20to%20have%20tap%20water%20supply%20in%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%20of%20announcement%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20in%20August%202019%2C%203.23%20crore%20(17%25)%20rural%20households%20were%20reported%20to%20have%20tap%20water%20connections%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20reply%20provided%20by%20the%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Jal%20Shakti%2C%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20States%2F%20UTs%20as%20on%2015.07.2023%2C%20additional%209.34%20Crore%20rural%20households%20have%20been%20provided%20with%20tap%20water%20connections%20under%20JJM.%20Thus%2C%20as%20on%2015.07.2023%2C%20out%20of%2019.46%20Crore%20rural%20households%20in%20the%20country%2C%20approx.%2012.57%20Crore%20(64.61%25)%20households%20are%20reported%20to%20have%20tap%20water%20supply%20in%20their%20homes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShekhawat%20added%20that%20as%20on%20July%2015%2C%202023%2C%20nine%20states%20and%20UTs%2C%20140%20districts%2C%201%2C432%20blocks%2C%2082%2C250%20gram%20panchayats%20and%201%2C72%2C757%20villages%20are%20reported%20as%20having%20come%20under%20%E2%80%98Har%20Ghar%20Jal%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20scheme%20in%20partnership%20with%20state%20governments%20had%20promised%20to%20make%20provision%20of%20tap%20water%20supply%20to%20every%20rural%20household%20by%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20Jal%20Shakti%20ministry%2C%20100%25%C2%A0%20of%20the%20rural%20households%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Dandra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20and%20Daman%20and%20Diu%2C%20Goa%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20have%20tap%20water%20supply%20as%20of%20July%2015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20reply%2C%20the%20states%20which%20have%20provided%20tap%20water%20to%20less%20than%2050%25%20of%20their%20rural%20households%20are%20West%20Bengal%20(34.23%25)%2C%20Jharkhand%20(38.64%25)%2C%20Rajasthan%20(40.96%25)%2C%20Kerala%20(49.73%25)%20and%20Lakshadweep%20(0)%2C%20as%20of%20July%2015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ministry%20data%20states%20that%20Delhi%20and%20Chandigarh%20do%20not%20have%20rural%20populations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-har-ghar-jal-by-2024%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20only%2075%25%20of%20households%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20water%20connection%20by%20March%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20delay%20was%20attributed%20in%20the%20report%20to%20several%20factors%2C%20including%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20slowed%20operations%2C%20and%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20caused%20a%20shortage%20in%20raw%20materials%20for%20manufacturing%20metal%20pipes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690282254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F02213735%2FTap-water.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdeadline-approaching-govt-says-only-64-6-rural-households-covered-under-har-ghar-jhal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parliament%20reply%20comes%20barely%20seven%20months%20after%20the%20government%20had%20announced%20in%20its%20year-end%20review%20that%20'Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20is%20on%20track%20to%20fulfil%20the%20government's%20resolve%20to%20provide%20tap%20water%20supply%20to%20every%20rural%20household%20by%202024.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdeadline-approaching-govt-says-only-64-6-rural-households-covered-under-har-ghar-jhal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20is%20Elon%20Musk's%20net%20worth%3F%20Find%20out%20the%20astonishing%20wealth%20of%20the%20tech%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226871%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20in%20a%20gray%20jacket%20and%20white%20dress%20shirt%20reacts%20in%20front%20of%20a%20purple%20and%20yellow%20step-repeat%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a2e1ed6075be0019c28193%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224581%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20the%20world's%20richest%20person.%3Cp%3EAlain%20Jocard%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETech%20mogul%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20net%20worth%20of%20%24239%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHis%20estimated%20fortune%20peaked%20at%20around%20%24340%20billion%20in%20November%202021%20as%20Tesla%20shares%20soared.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMusk%20is%20currently%20%2438%20million%20richer%20than%20LVMH's%20Bernard%20Arnault%2C%20the%20world's%20second-wealthiest%20person.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%2C%20has%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20around%20%24239%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20estimates%20by%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20tech%20mogul's%20wealth%20comes%20from%20a%20number%20of%20sources%20and%20it%20isn't%20stable.%20His%20fortunes%20have%20fluctuated%20greatly%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20he's%20been%20trading%20places%20with%20other%20tech%20billionaires%20to%20top%20Bloomberg's%20rich%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20has%20Musk's%20net%20worth%20changed%20over%20time%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20moved%20to%20Canada%2C%20and%20dropped%20out%20of%20a%20Ph.D%20at%20Stanford%2C%20became%20a%20millionaire%20before%20he%20hit%2030.%20Musk%20started%20Zip2%2C%20a%20website%20that%20provided%20city%20travel%20guides%20to%20newspapers%2C%20with%20his%20brother%20Kimbal%20Musk%2C%20and%20sold%20it%20to%20Compaq%20for%20more%20than%20%24300%20million%20in%201999.%20Musk%2C%20then%20aged%2027%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20got%20%2422%20million%20from%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20cofound%20online%20bank%20X.com%20in%201999.%20It%20soon%20merged%20with%20Peter%20Thiel's%20Confinity%20to%20become%20PayPal%2C%20and%20the%20company%20was%20bought%20for%20%241.5%20billion%20by%20eBay%20in%202002.%20Despite%20having%20been%20ousted%20as%20CEO%2C%20Musk%20walked%20away%20with%20around%20%24165%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20cofounded%20space-exploration%20company%20SpaceX%20in%202002.%20In%202004%2C%20he%20became%20an%20investor%20in%20and%20chairman%20of%20EV%20company%20Tesla.%20During%20the%20financial%20crisis%20in%202008%2C%20he%20saved%20Tesla%20from%20bankruptcy%20with%20a%20%2440%20million%20investment%20and%20a%20%2440%20million%20loan.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20he%20was%20named%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%202008%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20worst%20year%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%20Alongside%20problems%20in%20his%20personal%20life%2C%20Tesla%20kept%20losing%20money%20and%20SpaceX%20was%20having%20trouble%20launching%20its%20Falcon%201%20rocket.%20By%202009%2C%20Musk%20was%20living%20off%20personal%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Tesla%20went%20public%20in%202010%2C%20and%20Musk's%20estimated%20net%20worth%20steadily%20climbed.%20In%202012%20he%20debuted%20on%20Forbes'%20Billionaires%20List%20with%20an%20estimated%20wealth%20of%20%242%20billion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Musk%20set%20up%20tunnel-digging%20business%20the%20Boring%20Company.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20he%20founded%20neurotechnology%20startup%20Neuralink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20net%20worth%20began%20a%20rapid%20ascent%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pandemic%20as%20Tesla%20shares%20soared.%20Musk%20started%202020%20with%20an%20estimated%20net%20worth%20of%20just%20under%20%2430%20billion%20and%20was%20worth%20around%20%24170%20billion%20just%20a%20year%20later%20%E2%80%93%20a%20more%20than%20five-fold%20increase%20in%20just%20a%20year.%20His%20estimated%20fortune%20peaked%20at%20around%20%24340%20billion%20in%20November%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-no-longer-ceo-of-twitter-linda-yaccarino-starts-2023-6%5C%22%3Ebought%20Twitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%2444%20billion%20in%20October%202022%2C%20serving%20as%20its%20CEO%20until%20he%20stood%20down%20in%20early%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Bloomberg%20puts%20his%20current%20net%20worth%20at%20%24239%20billion%2C%20Forbes%20puts%20it%20at%20%24242.4%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhere%20does%20Musk's%20fortune%20come%20from%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20wealth%20is%20largely%20dependent%20on%20Tesla%20shares.%20Though%20he%20takes%20no%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-uri%3D%5C%22979cd34d269e8c4e648c693636110e47%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-salary-dropped-zero-2020-pay-electric-vehicles-2021-8%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https