20mother%20told%20me%20that%20this%20would%20not%20escalate%20to%20the%20point%20of%20killing%20each%20other%20and%20that%20things%20would%20be%20fine%20in%20a%20few%20days.%20I%20never%20thought%20she%20would%20be%20burnt%20alive%20the%20very%20next%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20not%20only%20did%20the%20militants%20attack%20Meitei%20villages%2C%20they%20also%20attacked%20the%20Sugnu%20police%20station%2C%20resulting%20in%20casualties%20amongst%20the%20security%20personnel.%20The%20community%20is%20also%20disappointed%20with%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20in%20the%20past%20two%20months%2C%20as%20they%20allege%20that%20the%20force%20is%20assisting%20Kuki%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Meitei%20villager%20who%20wishes%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20shared%20a%20video%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20showing%20Assam%20Rifles%20personnel%20surrounding%20the%20Sugnu%20police%20station%20and%20not%20allowing%20police%20personnel%20to%20leave.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20police%20questioned%20Assam%20Rifles%20jawans%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20whose%20order%20are%20you%20doing%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENL%2011C%200003%2C%20an%20olive%20green%20truck%2C%20can%20be%20seen%20standing%20outside%20the%20Sugnu%20police%20station%E2%80%99s%20main%20gate%20in%20the%20video.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20found%20out%20that%20the%20truck%20belongs%20to%20the%20director%20general%20of%20Assam%20Riffles%20and%20is%20registered%20in%20Kohima%2C%20Nagaland.%20Locals%20say%20that%20the%20video%20is%20from%20June%202.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20Assam%20Rifles%20to%20ask%20about%20this%20video.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20they%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25151704%2FIMG_4156.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25151704%2FIMG_4156.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25151704%2FIMG_4156-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25151704%2FIMG_4156-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664981%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIbetombi%E2%80%99s%20family%20performing%20her%20last%20rites.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2028%2C%20when%20alleged%20Kuki%20militants%20started%20burning%20houses%20in%20Serou%20village%2C%20everyone%20started%20running%20towards%20safety.%20Ibetombi%2C%20who%20was%2080%20years%20old%20and%20needed%20a%20stick%20to%20walk%2C%20could%20not%20run.%20According%20to%20the%20family%2C%20Ibetombi%20asked%20her%20daughter-in-law%20to%20leave%20her%20alone%20and%20come%20back%20later%20to%20take%20her%20with%20them%2C%20as%20she%20was%20confident%20that%20the%20Kuki%20militants%20would%20not%20kill%20her%20due%20to%20her%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ibetombi%E2%80%99s%20grandson%20found%20out%20that%20his%20grandmother%20was%20still%20inside%20the%20house%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20come%20back%20and%20try%20and%20save%20her%20life.%20But%20by%20the%20time%20he%20returned%2C%20he%20saw%20her%20burning%20in%20her%20house.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandmother%20used%20to%20live%20with%20her%20daughter-in-law%2C%20and%20I%20used%20to%20live%20with%20my%20wife%2C%20father%2C%20mother%20and%20sister.%20It%20was%202%20AM%20when%20our%20village%20got%20surrounded%20by%20Kuki%20militants%2C%20and%20they%20started%20firing%20into%20our%20houses.%20Everyone%20started%20running%2C%20but%20my%20grandmother%20couldn%E2%80%99t%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sarokhaibam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarokhaibam%20also%20suffered%20two%20bullet%20injuries%20and%20is%20recovering%20at%20RIMS%20Hospital%20in%20Imphal.%20He%20returned%20to%20save%20his%20grandmother%2C%20but%20by%20the%20time%20he%20reached%20Serou%2C%20he%20saw%20his%20house%20burning%2C%20and%20he%20received%20two%20bullet%20wounds%2C%20one%20on%20his%20hand%20and%20the%20other%20on%20his%20lower%20abdomen.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20my%20grandma%20is%20no%20more%2C%20and%20for%20the%20last%20rites%2C%20we%20only%20had%20her%20head%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sarokhaibam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarokhaibam%20also%20registered%20a%20separate%20FIR%20for%20his%20bullet%20injuries%2C%20but%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20police%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20parliament%20session%20began%20on%20July%2020%2C%20a%20video%20of%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20prompting%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20speak%20about%20Manipur.%20The%20Meitei%20community%20in%20Imphal%20says%20that%20once%20internet%20returns%20to%20the%20valley%2C%20there%20will%20be%20thousands%20of%20videos%20showing%20their%20people%20being%20killed%20by%20Kuki%20militants%2C%20which%20they%20want%20to%20share%20with%20the%20prime%20minister.%20The%20community%20shared%20two%20such%20purported%20videos%20of%20brutal%20killings%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChurachandra%20has%20appealed%20to%20both%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20this%20violence.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20go%20back%20to%20our%20village%20and%20live%20there%20again.%20The%20government%20should%20arrange%20for%20our%20safety%20and%20provide%20security%20to%20all%20the%20villagers.%E2%80%9D%20As%20the%20son%20of%20a%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20he%20wants%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20take%20notice%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20provide%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690279489000%2C%22visual%22%3A%