%20the%20By%20Rotation%20app.%3Cp%3ECharlie%20Hollishead%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20investor%20relations%20for%20mining%20companies%20and%20teach%20Pilates%20on%20the%20side.%20I'm%20trying%20to%20move%20out%20of%20corporate%20and%20more%20into%20the%20Pilates%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20heard%20of%20By%20Rotation%20earlier%20in%20the%20pandemic.%20I%20downloaded%20the%20app%20when%20it%20was%20still%20very%20new.%20I%20listed%20two%20items%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Prada%20bag%20and%20a%20Zimmermann%20dress%20%E2%80%94%20but%20didn't%20think%20too%20much%20of%20it.%20One%20week%20later%2C%20I%20got%20a%20notification%20that%20someone%20had%20requested%20to%20rent%20something.%20I%20remember%20being%20so%20excited.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20more%20and%20more%20people%20got%20on%20the%20app.%20Now%20I%20have%20about%2080%20items%20listed%20and%20get%20requests%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20ideal%20app%20for%20me%20because%20I've%20always%20loved%20buying%20dresses.%20But%20I%20don't%20know%20where%20I%20think%20I'm%20going%20to%20wear%20all%20of%20them.%20I%20don't%20go%20out%20that%20much.%20I'm%20happy%20that%20someone%20can%20put%20them%20to%20good%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20spend%20the%20money%20that%20I%20make%20from%20By%20Rotation%20on%20buying%20new%20clothes.%20My%20monthly%20salary%20goes%20toward%20my%20general%20living%20expenses%2C%20and%20I%20use%20the%20money%20from%20the%20app%20to%20help%20fund%20my%20Pilates%20training%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20a%20rental%20on%20the%20By%20Rotation%20app%20works%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22clothing%20hangs%20on%20a%20garment%20rack%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bad0d503c40c001a9839c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221155%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHollishead%20suggests%20writing%20thorough%20descriptions%20of%20each%20item%20you%20rent%20out.%3Cp%3ECharlie%20Hollishead%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20rent%20an%20item%20of%20clothing%2C%20you%20upload%20photos%20of%20you%20wearing%20it%2C%20or%20you%20can%20use%20product%20photos%20from%20online.%20You%20add%20the%20brand%2C%20the%20size%2C%20and%20a%20description%20to%20the%20listing.%20You%20should%20let%20people%20know%20if%20there's%20any%20damage%20or%20if%20you've%20had%20it%20altered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20you%20input%20the%20retail%20value%20of%20the%20item%2C%20and%20the%20app%20suggests%20a%20rental%20price.%20For%20an%20item%20that's%20worth%20about%20%C2%A3200%2C%20its%20suggestion%20will%20be%20about%20%C2%A310%20a%20day.%20By%20Rotation%20suggests%20that%20you%20set%20the%20minimum%20rental%20period%20at%20three%20days.%20Once%20By%20Rotation%20accepts%20the%20item%2C%20people%20can%20find%20it%20through%20search%2C%20or%20they%20can%20go%20directly%20to%20your%20profile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20someone%20wants%20to%20rent%20your%20item%2C%20they%20send%20you%20a%20request%20with%20the%20dates%20and%20where%20they%20plan%20to%20wear%20it.%20You%20can%20either%20accept%20or%20decline%2C%20and%20when%20the%20rental%20goes%20through%2C%20By%20Rotation%20takes%2015%25%20of%20the%20total%20rental%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20rental%2C%20they%20can%20collect%20it%20from%20your%20house.%20I've%20also%20had%20people%20come%20to%20my%20office.%20You%20can%20also%20just%20ship%20it%20out%20to%20them.%20Once%20the%20rental's%20over%2C%20they%20send%20it%20back%2C%20and%20you%20get%20paid%20within%20about%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20nervous%20about%20renting%20my%20designer%20clothes%20to%20strangers.%20But%20I've%20made%20friends%20on%20the%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charlie%20Hollishead%20wears%20a%20pink%20dress%20posing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20black%20wall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bad12e03c40c001a983a74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHollishead%20said%20she%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20repeat%20customers%20renting%20from%20her%20often.%3Cp%3ECharlie%20Hollishead%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20being%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BAm%20I%20ever%20going%20to%20see%20this%20again%3F%26quot%3B%20At%20first%2C%20I%20was%20very%20scared%20about%20it.%20But%20everyone%20on%20the%20app%20is%20so%20friendly%2C%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20have%20used%20it%20a%20few%20times%2C%20you%20feel%20less%20nervous%20about%20renting%20things%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20meet%20someone%20face-to-face%2C%20that%20automatically%20puts%20you%20at%20ease%20because%20you've%20met%20the%20person%20you're%20handing%20the%20item%20over%20to.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20people%20renting%20from%20me%2C%20I%20think%20they%20feel%20comfortable%20because%20I've%20gotten%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20there%20are%20loads%20of%20people%20joining%20the%20app%2C%20so%20if%20a%20person%20doesn't%20have%20any%20reviews%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20they're%20not%20legit.%20It%20might%20just%20be%20that%20they've%20just%20joined%20the%20platform%2C%20so%20it's%20just%20having%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20conversation%20with%20them%20beforehand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20made%20a%20few%20friends%20just%20by%20being%20on%20the%20app.%20One%20of%20the%20girls%20who%20rented%20one%20of%20my%20items%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20dinner%20with%20her%20next%20week.%20It's%20such%20a%20nice%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%20I%20see%20the%20dresses%20I%20buy%20as%20investments.%20They%20pay%20for%20themselves%2C%20and%20then%20some.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22863%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charlie%20May%20poses%20in%20a%20green%20dress%20with%20feather%20hem%5C%22%20