risis.%20If%20anything%2C%20it%20made%20Britain%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20all%20of%20these%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20actually%2C%20the%20departure%20of%20many%20immigrant%20communities%20has%20actually%20harmed%20their%20economy%20in%20so%20many%20ways%20because%20now%20the%20service%20sector%2C%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20is%20struggling%20to%20find%20people%20to%20do%20jobs.%20I%20think%C2%A0that%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20making%20the%20electorate%20smarter%20and%20better%20equipped%20to%20interrogate%20the%20idea%20that%20there%20are%20quick%20fixes%20to%20any%20of%20these%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobally%2C%20authors%20of%20colour%20are%20gaining%20visibility.%20Do%20you%20think%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20in%20name%20or%20has%20that%20actually%20affected%20how%20you%20are%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20author%20from%20a%20non-white%20background%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20fact%20that%20authors%2C%C2%A0academics%20and%C2%A0filmmakers%20with%20Black%20heritage%20have%20become%20more%20visible.%20That%E2%80%99s%20partly%20just%20the%20backlog%20of%20having%20been%20squeezed%20out%20of%20having%20a%20platform%20and%20having%20no%20opportunity%20for%20so%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20also%20think%20it%20does%20reflect%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20do%20have%20access%20to%20more%20information%2C%20and%20they%20are%20able%20to%20find%20the%20stories%20that%20they%20want.%20It%20is%20becoming%20more%20of%20a%20marketplace%2C%20whereas%20in%20the%20past%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20information%20we%20had%20access%20to%20was%20so%20heavily%20controlled%20by%20white%20gatekeepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20take%20something%20like%20the%20death%20of%20the%20Queen%2C%20the%20British%20media%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20police%20the%20media%20response%20to%20that%2C%20whereas%20now%20we%20hear%20voices%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20from%20India%2C%20from%20Australia%2C%20fro