%2Findia-news%2Fcall-us-whatever-you-want-mr-modi-we-will-rahul-gandhi-rebuts-pm-modi-4239075%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Gorakhpur%2C%20a%20Tussle%20Within%20the%20Nishad%20Community%20Challenges%20Sanjay%20Nishad's%20Monopoly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25142320%2FUntitled-design-12-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGorakhpur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20tussle%20for%20Nishad%20votes%20has%20once%20again%20started%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Gorakhpur%20with%20the%20announcement%20of%20a%20Nishad%20Mahakumbh%20on%20July%2024%20to%20challenge%20the%20monopoly%20of%20the%20NISHAD%20Party%20on%20the%20Nishad%20community.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20organiser%20of%20this%20Mahakumbh%2C%20Jai%20Prakash%20Nishad%2C%20is%20a%20former%20member%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20who%20left%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20to%20join%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20Foremost%20among%20issues%20that%20Jai%20Prakash%20is%20keen%20to%20mobilise%20the%20community%20on%20is%20the%20reservation%20for%20Nishads.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Nishad%20(an%20acronym%20for%20Nirbal%20Indian%20Shoshit%20Hamara%20Aam%20Dal)%20Party%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20Jai%20Prakash%20Nishad%20has%20been%20in%20the%20BJP%20for%20some%20time%20now.%20The%20announcement%2C%20however%2C%20has%20led%20to%20a%20war%20of%20words%20between%20the%20Nishad%20party%20and%20Jai%20Prakash.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20Nishad%20party%20leaders%20have%20said%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20Nishad%20Mahakumbh%20have%20turned%20their%20backs%20on%20the%20Nishad%20community%2C%20the%20latter%20are%20calling%20Nishad%20party%20president%20Dr.%20Sanjay%20Nishad%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdealer%E2%80%9D%20of%20Nishad%20votes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20scene%20was%20witnessed%20at%20the%20Circuit%20House%20on%20Friday%2C%20July%2021%2C%20when%20Nishad%20party%20workers%20raised%20loud%20slogans%20at%20Jai%20Prakash%E2%80%99s%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESanjay%20Nishad%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20time%20and%20presented%20a%20letter%20written%20ostensibly%20in%20blood%20addressed%20to%20the%20Nishad%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20drop%20of%20blood%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20fishermen%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CReservation%20for%20Nishad%20community%20is%20at%20a%20very%20crucial%20stage.%20The%20central%20government%20will%20soon%20clarify%20its%20position%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20reservation.%20Opposition%20leaders%20are%20upset%20with%20the%20steps%20taken%20on%20Majhwar%20and%20Tureha%20reservation.%20Today%2C%20those%20who%20got%20the%20reservation%20file%20stolen%20are%20trying%20to%20mislead%20the%20society%20in%20the%20name%20of%20reservation.%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20debate%20the%20issue%20of%20reservation%20in%20an%20open%20forum.%20The%20time%20and%20place%20can%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20opposition%20leaders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20and%20rise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Nishad%20party%20has%20witnessed%20a%20meteoric%20rise%20in%20a%20short%20span%20of%20seven%20years.%20Today%2C%20it%20has%20six%20MLAs%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Sanjay%20Nishad%E2%80%99s%20elder%20son%20Praveen%20is%20a%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Santkabir%20Nagar%20while%20younger%20son%20Sarwan%20is%20an%20MLA%20from%20Chaurichaura.%20Sanjay%20is%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20in%20the%20UP%20government.%20Now%2C%20his%20third%20son%2C%20Dr.%20Amit%2C%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20launch%20his%20political%20career.%20He%20is%20frequently%20seen%20in%20the%20programmes%20of%20the%20party%20and%20has%20been%20made%20the%20working%20president%20of%20the%20Nishad%20Ekta%20Parishad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESanjay%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20extend%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20reach%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20beyond.%20Recently%20he%20visited%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20In%20the%20municipal%20elections%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20field%20Nishad%20party%20candidates%20in%20many%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20something%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20pay%20heed%20to.%20More%20than%20half%20a%20dozen%20candidates%20of%20Nishad%20party%20jumped%20into%20the%20fray%20despite%20having%20been%20instructed%20not%20to%20contest%20the%20elections.%20Sanjay%20has%20purportedly%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20getting%20more%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20but%20with%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20Bhartiya%20Samaj%20Party%20joining%20the%20NDA%2C%20this%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20uphill%20task.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-fully-assured-caste-census-demands-will-be-met-by-bjp-o-p-rajbhar%5C%22%3EInterview%20%7C%20%E2%80%98Fully%20Assured%20Caste%20Census%20Demands%20Will%20Be%20Met%20by%20BJP%E2%80%99%3A%20O.P.%20Rajbhar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sanjay%20is%20also%20facing%20hurdles%20in%20his%20own%20stronghold.%20During%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20an%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20cut%20his%20vote%20share%20by%20floating%20a%20political%20party%20named%20Sarvahara%20Vikas%20Party.%20Mukesh%20Sahni%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Vikassheel%20Insaan%20Party%20(VIP)%20also%20tried%20to%20obstruct%20his%20straight%20path%20to%20success%20by%20fielding%20candidates%20in%20Nishad-dominated%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20had%20also%20fielded%20several%20Nishad%20candidates%20in%20Gorakhpur%20and%20neighbouring%20districts%20but%20none%20of%20them%20could%20secure%20a%20win.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAttempts%20to%20dampen%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20spirits%20had%20not%20been%20successful%20as%20he%20managed%20to%20win%20six%20out%20of%2010%20assembly%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20had%20given%2016%20seats%20to%20the%20Nishad%20Party%2C%20in%20which%2010%20candidates%20fought%20under%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20Nishad%20Party%20while%20six%20contested%20on%20the%20BJP%20symbol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2013%2C%202023%2C%20through%20a%20grand%20event%20to%20celebrate%20the%2010th%20Sankalp%20Divas%2C%20Sanjay%20attempted%20to%20establish%20himself%20as%20the%20sole%20leader%20of%20the%20Nishad%20community.%20The%20ceremony%20took%20place%20at%20Mahant%20Digvijaynath%20Park%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20Ramgarh%20Tal%20in%20Gorakhpur.%20Chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20was%20also%20present.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDocumentaries%20were%20screened%20to%20highlight%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20achievements.%20He%20was%20hailed%20as%20%E2%80%98Mahamana%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98supremo%20of%20Nishad%20party%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98political%20godfather%20of%20the%20fishermen%E2%80%99.%20A%20garland%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20in%20currency%20notes%20was%20presented%20to%20him%2C%20along%20with%20a%20vehicle%20worth%20Rs%2051%20lakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20other%20political%20parties%2C%20especially%20the%20SP%2C%20are%20constantly%20trying%20to%20challenge%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20growing%20political%20clout%2C%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20sideline%20him%20within%20the%20BJP%20as%20well.%20His%20frequent%20photo%20ops%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20have%20irked%20several%20influential%20BJP%20leaders.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25134022%2FF0f5GcYagAA_9ek.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25134022%2FF0f5GcYagAA_9ek.jpeg%201125w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25134022%2FF0f5GcYagAA_9ek-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25134022%2FF0f5GcYagAA_9ek-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664959%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Nishad%20greets%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40mahamana4u%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Purvanchal%2C%20granting%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20to%20Nishad%20party%20candidates%20has%20also%20miffed%20many.%20It%20seems%20that%20a%20lobby%20within%20the%20BJP%20has%20put%20forth%20Jai%20Prakash%20in%20order%20to%20curtail%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20rise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20challenger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJai%20Prakash%20Nishad%20was%20a%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20MLA%20from%20Chauri%20Chaura%20between%202012%20and%202017.%20The%20former%20BSP%20government%20had%20even%20appointed%20him%20as%20a%20Minister%20of%20State.%20He%20contested%20the%202017%20election%20from%20Chauri%20Chaura%20on%20a%20BSP%20ticket%20again%20but%20lost%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Sangeeta%20Yadav.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20the%20time%20when%20the%20Nishad%20Party%20contested%20the%20assembly%20elections%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20It%20had%20then%20allied%20with%20Dr.%20Ayub%E2%80%99s%20Peace%20Party%20and%20contested%20on%2072%20seats.%20It%20won%20only%20one%20seat%20%E2%80%93%20Gyanpur%20%E2%80%93%20but%20received%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20votes%20%E2%80%93%20a%20total%20of%205%2C40%2C539%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fknown-for-its-meteoric-rise-can-ups-nishad-party-repeat-the-feat-this-time%5C%22%3EKnown%20for%20Its%20Meteoric%20Rise%2C%20Is%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Nishad%20Party%20Set%20for%20Success%20This%20Time%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20by-election%20was%20held%20on%20the%20Gorakhpur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20and%20the%20SP%20nominated%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20son%20Praveen.%20He%20also%20got%20the%20support%20of%20BSP%2C%20Peace%20Party%20and%20others%20and%20took%20everyone%20by%20surprise%20when%20he%20defeated%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20in%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20bastion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20by-election%20result%20was%20widely%20discussed%20across%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20soon%20realised%20that%20Nishad%20votes%20were%20drifting%20away%20from%20it.%20So%2C%20Jai%20Prakash%20was%20brought%20on%20board%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%202018%20to%20bring%20back%20Nishad%20votes.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20in%202020%2C%20the%20BJP%20made%20him%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20on%20the%20seat%20vacated%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Beniprasad%20Verma.%20Nishad%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20a%20little%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20completed%20his%20tenure%20quietly%20and%20no%20special%20activism%20was%20witnessed%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20may%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20before%20being%20appointed%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%2C%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Nishad%20Party%20broke%20up%20with%20the%20SP%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20closeness%20with%20BJP%20kept%20increasing%20and%20the%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20started%20giving%20preference%20to%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJai%20Prakash%E2%80%99s%20sudden%20activism%20in%20his%20decision%20to%20organise%20the%20Nishad%20Mahakumbh%20before%20the%20next%20year%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20has%20shocked%20political%20analysts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Jai%20Prakash%20is%20not%20very%20vocal%20and%20has%20the%20image%20of%20a%20soft%20leader.%20He%20has%20a%20close%20association%20with%20the%20Nishad%20community%20but%20has%20never%20showed%20great%20ambition.%20He%20is%20also%20not%20considered%20an%20aggressive%20leader%20like%20Rambhual%20Nishad%2C%20Amarendra%20Nishad%20and%20Kajal%20Nishad%20of%20SP.%20He%20maintains%20friendly%20ties%20with%20leaders%20across%20party%20lines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20event%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20present%2C%20Jai%20Prakash%20is%20touring%20Gorakhpur%20and%20other%20neighbouring%20districts%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Nishad%20Mahakumbh%20and%20claims%20that%20it%20will%20have%20a%20record%20gathering.%20Many%20veteran%20Nishad%20leaders%20are%20seen%20with%20him%20on%20these%20tours.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20Ghanshyama%20Dutt%20Nishad%2C%20said%20that%20all%20the%20castes%20and%20sub-castes%20of%20the%20Nishads%20will%20demand%20Scheduled%20Caste%20reservation%20for%20the%20community%20in%20the%20Mahakumbh.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20setting%20up%20a%20separate%20commission%20for%20the%20denotified%20castes%20will%20also%20be%20made.%20He%20said%20that%20if%20the%20Nishad%20community%20does%20not%20get%20their%20constitutional%20right%2C%20then%20the%20BJP%20will%20face%20severe%20opposition%20in%20the%202024%20elections%20from%20them.%20They%20plan%20to%20give%20an%20ultimatum%20of%20three%20months%20to%20the%20state%20and%20Union%20government%20before%20beginning%20protests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20being%20asked%20why%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20Nishad%20community%20have%20not%20been%20met%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20chief%20organiser%20of%20the%20Nishad%20Mahakumbh%2C%20Jai%20Prakash%2C%20is%20a%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Nishad%20party%20is%20also%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Jai%20Prakash%20has%20always%20raised%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20community%20at%20his%20own%20level.%20But%20this%20time%20the%20Nishad%20community%20wants%20to%20warn%20the%20BJP%20through%20the%20Mahakumbh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Nishad%20community%20has%20rejected%20Sanjay%20Nishad%20as%20their%20leader%20and%20no%20longer%20expect%20anything%20from%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20talks%20about%20reservation%20when%20he%20is%20with%20us%20but%20when%20he%20meets%20prominent%20leaders%20of%20the%20government%2C%20he%20does%20not%20raise%20the%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20them%2C%20he%20only%20discusses%20prospects%20for%20himself%20and%20his%20family%20members.%20He%20has%20served%20his%20platter%20full%20of%20food%20(the%20election%20symbol%20of%20the%20Nishad%20party)%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20eat%20from.%20BJP%20leaders%20contest%20elections%20on%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20Nishad%20party%20and%20tickets%20are%20sold%20off.%20Now%2C%20he%20is%20left%20only%20with%20paid%20workers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Mahakumbh%20organisers%20have%20said%20that%20no%20flag%20of%20any%20political%20party%20will%20be%20hoisted%20in%20the%20event%20and%20there%20will%20be%20no%20speech%20for%20or%20against%20any%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJai%20Prakash%20Nishad%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CNishad%20Mahakumbh%20is%20not%20an%20event%20organised%20for%20any%20political%20party%20or%20organisation%20but%20the%20entire%20Nishad%20community.%20Through%20this%20event%2C%20we%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20government%20that%20they%20should%20directly%20address%20the%20community%20regarding%20the%20demands.%20We%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20any%20middleman%20who%20bargains%20our%20votes%20for%20favours%20for%20his%20own%20family%20members.%20BJP%20gave%2016%20tickets%20to%20Nishad%20party%20but%20they%20were%20not%20given%20to%20those%20who%20struggled%20for%20the%20community.%20This%20has%20caused%20a%20lot%20of%20disappointment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJai%20Prakash%20also%20added%20that%20the%20community%20is%20not%20angry%20with%20the%20BJP.%20All%20they%20want%20is%20to%20get%20their%20rights%20directly%20and%20not%20through%20any%20middlemen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJai%20Prakash%20claimed%20that%20the%20crowd%20that%20is%20going%20to%20gather%20at%20the%20Mahakumbh%20will%20break%20all%20records.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20reaction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20announcement%20for%20the%20mega%20event%20has%20caused%20unease%20in%20the%20Nishad%20party%20as%20indicated%20in%20party%20president%20Sanjay%E2%80%99s%20address%20to%20party%20workers%20on%20July%2021.%20Without%20naming%20Jai%20Prakash%2C%20he%20called%20him%20a%20%E2%80%98traitor%2C%20Vibhishan%20and%20a%20snake%20in%20the%20grass%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20Nishad%20community%20and%20asked%20his%20fellow%20community%20members%20to%20drive%20such%20people%20out.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20whole%20exercise%20is%20to%20get%20the%20%E2%80%98elephant%20partner%E2%80%99%20(referring%20to%20the%20BSP)%20a%20seat.%20He%20said%20that%20any%20leader%20who%20opposes%20the%20lotus%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20platter%20full%20of%20food%20(Nishad%20party)%20can%20never%20belong%20to%20the%20Nishad%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20honoured%20me%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20fishermen%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%20comes%20in%20my%20way%2C%20perishes.%20A%20%E2%80%98Bihari%20%3Cem%3Ebhai%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20had%20also%20surfaced%20in%202016.%20Look%20at%20the%20condition%20he%20is%20in%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20allegations%20of%20nepotism%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20members%20of%20our%20family%20are%20aboard%20this%20train%20(of%20struggle).%20They%20have%20been%20beaten%20up%20for%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Nishad%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENishad%20party%20has%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20organised%20several%20major%20rallies%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20Ramgarh%20Tal.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Sanjay%20has%20been%20directly%20challenged%20the%20symbolic%20action%20of%20Nishad%20leaders%20organising%20a%20Nishad%20Mahakumbh%20at%20the%20same%20venue.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Hindi%20original%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690276856000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25142320%2FUntitled-design-12-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnishad-sanjay-jai-prakash-gorakhpur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20organiser%20of%20a%20Nishad%20Mahakumbh%2C%20Jai%20Prakash%20Nishad%2C%20is%20a%20former%20BJP%20man%20who%20is%20taking%20on%20Sanjay%20Nishad%2C%20the%20influential%20leader%20of%20BJP's%20ally%2C%20Nishad%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnishad-sanjay-jai-prakash-gorakhpur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Government%20Orders%20Inspection%20of%20Eros%20International%E2%80%99s%20Accounts%20After%20Damning%20Report%20by%20Regulators%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690276616000%2C%22visual