0that%20like%20once%20a%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Naqvee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20hard%20clothing%20businesses%20try%2C%20online%20purchases%20always%20leave%20room%20for%20error%2C%20which%20is%20why%20retail%20fashion%20has%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fforecasts%2F997848%2Fmost-returned-online-purchases-by-category-in-the-uk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighest%20rate%20of%20online%20purchases%20returned%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetailers%20are%20likely%20to%20see%20deshopping%20and%20bracketing%20as%20minor%20issues%20if%20managed%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1362%2F026725708X273993%3FneedAccess%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20a%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Marketing%20Management%20in%202010%2C%20companies%20are%20%26quot%3Bdeliberately%20blinkered%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20addressing%20the%20wardrobing%20issue.%20Some%20even%20see%20deshoppers%20as%20more%20valuable%20customers%20than%20those%20who%20return%20products%20due%20to%20genuine%20reasons%2C%20such%20as%20wrong%20sizing%20or%20poor-quality%20material.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emerald.com%2Finsight%2Fcontent%2Fdoi%2F10.1108%2FIJPDLM-10-2019-0302%2Ffull%2Fhtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20more%20recent%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%202021%20looked%20at%20planned%20versus%20unplanned%20returns%20and%20showed%20that%20lenient%20return%20policies%20can%20boost%20sales%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20compensates%20for%20the%20costs%20associated%20with%20processing%20returned%20products.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShoppers%20who%20plan%20to%20return%20the%20goods%20from%20the%20beginning%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20loyal%20customers.%20Today%2C%20c