n-exile-asks-refugees-in-india-to-stay-away-from-political-ethnic-conflicts%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0earlier%2C%20several%20political%20leaders%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Meitei%20community%20have%20accused%20Myanmarese%20military%20groups%20of%20supporting%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20against%20persons%20belonging%20to%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20majority%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20share%20a%20porous%20border%20with%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Chin%20state.%20The%20Kukis%20and%20Mizos%20share%20a%20common%20ancestry%20with%20the%20Chins%20of%20Myanmar%20and%20inhabit%20that%20contiguous%20landmass%20across%20the%20international%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20India%20and%20Myanmar%20have%20a%20free%20movement%20regime%20(FMR)%20in%20place%20within%2016%20kms%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border.%20However%2C%20this%20has%20been%20temporarily%20suspended%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20groups%20have%20been%20claiming%20since%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20state%20that%20even%20large-scale%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigration%E2%80%9D%20from%20Myanmar%20has%20been%20playing%20a%20part%20in%20the%20ongoing%20crisis%20in%20the%20state.%20Even%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20accused%20Kukis%20in%20Churachandpur%20of%20illegally%20sheltering%20immigrants%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20which%20also%20angered%20Kukis%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2015%2C%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20government-in-exile%2C%20the%20National%20Unity%20Government%20(NUG)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmyanmar-govt-in-exile-asks-refugees-in-india-to-stay-away-from-political-ethnic-conflicts%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20Myanmarese%20citizens%2C%20who%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Ctemporarily%20sheltering%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%20due%20to%20the%20military%20crackdown%20in%20that%20country%2C%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20local%20political%20matters%20and%20ethnic-based%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NUG%20government%E2%80%99s%20advisory%20to%20the%20displaced%20citizens%20is%20significant%20because%20it%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20majority%20Meitei%20community%20is%20claiming%20involvement%20of%20Myanmarese%20nationals%20in%20their%20ongoing%20clash%20with%20the%20Kuki%20community%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20estimates%2C%20over%2040%2C000%20people%20from%20Myanmar%20have%20been%20living%20in%20Mizoram%20and%20Manipur%20as%20refugees%20since%20the%20military%20coup%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20in%20February%202021.%20The%20Manipur%20government%20has%20constituted%20a%20Population%20Commission%20to%20implement%20a%20drive%20against%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20can%20confirm%20that%20Assam%20Rifles%20has%20been%20guarding%20political%20refugees%20of%20Myanmar%20at%20an%20Aizawl%20locality%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20where%20the%20state%20government%20went%20against%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20directive%20to%20push%20them%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690275152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2F13255950_1321836797843953_6178772345842836481_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fclarify-why-and-how-manipur-govt-to-assam-rifles-on-718-myanmar-nationals-who-entered-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20the%20Myanmar%20nationals%20entered%20Manipur%20on%20July%2022-23%20without%20proper%20travel%20documents.%20Although%20India%20and%20Myanmar%20have%20a%20free%20movement%20regime%2C%20it%20has%20been%20suspended%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fclarify-why-and-how-manipur-govt-to-assam-rifles-on-718-myanmar-nationals-who-entered-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Not%20Taxing%20Recreational%20Ones%5C%22%3A%20Official%20Explains%2028%25%20GST%20On%20Online%20Gaming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20reason%20to%20lower%20excise%20duty%20on%20petroleum%20products%2C%20Revenue%20Secretary%20Sanjay%20Malhotra%20told%20NDTV%20today%2C%20explaining%20that%20it%20was%20already%20done%20twice%20when%20crude%20prices%20were%20at%20their%20peak.%20Crude%20prices%20have%20since%20softened%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20proposal%20for%20further%20reduction%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20taxing%20online%20gaming%2C%20he%20said%20they%20haven't%20recieved%20any%20specific%20written%20proposal%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20well%20considered%20decision%20by%20GST%20and%20we%20have%20done%20this%20after%20lots%20of%20discussion.%20We%20have%20spoken%20and%20met%20%C2%A0to%20the%20online%20gaming%20industry%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Malhotra%20said%20about%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20Council%20announcing%20it%20will%20levy%20a%2028%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20online%20games%20involving%20real%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20communication.%20We%20are%20not%20taxing%20recreational%20games.%20Where%20there%20is%20no%20money%20involved%2C%20taxes%20will%20remain%20at%2018%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnline%20gaming%20players%20have%20expressed%20disappointment%20with%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20Council.%20The%20government%20may%20request%20the%20GST%20Council%20to%20consider%20the%20facts%20of%20new%20regulatory%20framework%20for%20the%20industry%2C%20Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20last%20week%2C%20revealing%20that%20it%20took%20three%20years%20for%20the%20Council%20to%20reach%20a%20decision%20on%20online%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGamers%20have%20said%20that%20levying%2028%20per%20cent%20GST%20on%20Gross%20Gaming%20Revenue%20(GGR)%20or%20the%20platform%20fee%20results%20in%20around%201%2C000%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20tax%20on%20the%20industry%20and%20cause%20irreversible%20damage%20to%20the%20USD%202.5%20billion%20investments%20in%20the%20Indian%20online%20gaming%20startup%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Malhotra%20said%20the%20gamers'%20concerns%20will%20be%20taken%20into%20account%20by%20the%20GST%20Council%2C%20and%20clarified%20that%20the%2028%20per%20cent%20taxation%20will%20not%20be%20on%20the%20GGR%2C%20but%20on%20%26quot%3Bface%20value%26quot%3B.%20Whether%20the%20tax%20will%20be%20at%20entry%20level%20or%20at%20every%20bet%20pool%20will%20soon%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20Council%2C%20Sanjay%20Malhotra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Malhotra%20also%20put%20to%20rest%20speculations%20around%20whether%20the%20deadline%20for%20filing%20income%20tax%20returns%20will%20be%20extended%2C%20like%20every%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20extension.%20We%20are%20doing%20much%20better%20than%20last%20year%2C%20and%20I%20see%20no%20reason%20to%20delay%20or%20extend%2C%20and%20urge%20everyone%20to%20file%20their%20tax%20returns%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverseas%20ordinary%20purchases%20like%20an%20OTT%20subscription%2C%20news%20subscription%20etc%20are%20not%20under%20the%20Liberalised%20Remittance%20Scheme%20(LRS).%20%26quot%3BOnly%20remittances%20made%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20investments%2C%20education%2C%20tourism%2C%20medical%20expenses%20etc.%20are%20under%20LRS%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20only%20spends%20over%20Rs%207%20lakh%20are%20taxed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELRS%2C%20aimed%20to%20facilitate%20hassle-free%20foreign%20exchange%2C%20is%20a%20scheme%20that%20enables%20Indian%20residents%20to%20remit%20funds%20abroad%20for%20certain%20specified%20purposes.%20Any%20remittance%20over%20%242.5%20lakh%20or%20its%20equivalent%20in%20a%20foreign%20currency%20will%20need%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India's%20(RBI)%20approval%2C%20the%20earlier%20limit%20was%20%2425%2C000.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20usage%20of%20international%20credit%20cards%20(ICCs)%20for%20making%20payments%20for%20fulfilling%20expenses%20during%20travel%20outside%20India%20was%20not%20included%20in%20the%20LRS%20limit%20but%20this%20too%20has%20changed%20as%20the%20government%20suspected%20tax%20evasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Budget%202023-24%20hiked%20TCS%20(tax%20deducted%20at%20source)%20rates%20to%2020%25%2C%20from%205%25%20currently%2C%20on%20overseas%20tour%20packages%20and%20funds%20remitted%20under%20LRS%20(other%20than%20for%20education%20and%20medical%20purposes).%20The%20new%20tax%20rates%20came%20into%20effect%20from%20July%201%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mostly%20affects%20high%20net%20worth%20people%20who%20spend%20huge%20sums%20in%20investments%20using%20their%20credit%20cards%20and%20those%20who%20buy%20very%20expensive%20gifts%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20a%20flight%26quot%3B%2C%20we%20taxed%20foreign%20remmitances%20at%20source%20at%2020%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20the%20credit%20card%20international%20spend%20is%20at%2020%20per%20cent%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTax%20buoyancy%20is%20good%2C%20and%20we%20will%20meet%20our%20targets%20despite%20economic%20growth%20slowing%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Revenue%20Secretary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690275120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fsmhcbnkg_revenue-secretary-sanjay-malhotra_625x300_25_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgst-on-online-gaming-itr-extension-2023-liberalised-remittance-scheme-lrs-not-taxing-recreational-games-revenue-