20which%20allows%20for%20a%20short-duration%20discussion%20on%20a%20particular%20issue%20not%20exceeding%20two-and-a-half%20hours%2C%20Mr%20Dhankar%20said%20the%20Trinamool%20MP%20rightly%20pointed%20out%20that%20all%20176%20notices%20can%20be%20overruled%20if%20Rule%20267%20notices%20are%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20government%20is%20not%20expecting%20the%20opposition%20to%20back%20down%20from%20its%20demand%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20speak%20in%20parliament%20on%20the%20Manipur%20issue%2C%20and%20it%20will%20now%20insist%20on%20settling%20its%20legislative%20work.%20If%20a%20bill%20has%20to%20be%20passed%20amid%20uproar%2C%20it%20will%20be%20done%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20chaired%20a%20parliamentary%20meeting%20of%20the%20BJP%20this%20morning%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-mujahideens-name-also-has-india-pm-attacks-opposition-front-4238919%5C%22%3Ehe%20lambasted%20the%20Opposition%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI've%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20directionless%20opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20party%20sources.%20Just%20using%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20name%20doesn't%20mean%20anything%2C%20the%20PM%20reportedly%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20East%20India%20Company%20and%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20too%20have%20India%20in%20their%20names.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20opposition%20MPs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-mps-sit-on-night-protest-outside-parliament-amid-manipur-tangle-4238168%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20statue%20at%20Parliament%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20last%20night%20in%20protest%20against%20disruption%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20for%20a%20third%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20said%20parliament%20did%20not%20function%20for%20a%20third%20day%20because%20of%20the%20%26quot