%20who%20was%20deployed%20in%20the%20Goa%20Operation%20of%20Liberation%20of%20Anjediva%20Island%20in%20December%201961%2C%20and%20was%20injured%20when%20his%20motorboat%20came%20under%20fire%2C%20has%20finally%20been%20told%20that%20he%20will%20be%20receiving%20compensation%20for%20the%20injury%20he%20received%20in%20combat.%20The%20bullet%20that%20struck%20Tara%20Singh%2C%20now%2083%20years%20old%2C%20is%20still%20lodged%20in%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fpunjab%2Fbullet-still-in-head-ex-sailor-gets-war-injury-pension-after-60-yrs-528637%3F_gl%3D1*1kh6p3g*_ga*OUJWNVBJbWNyV25nSlBsSy1ONHk2QkVDS3lXaXVOWi1mMzFhdFdUdE5mVHdqZ3FQd0xqREZpMjJnU0VidnA0dg%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Chandigarh%20Bench%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Tribunal%20has%20said%20that%20Singh%20must%20be%20paid%20a%20war%20injury%20pension.%20%E2%80%9COn%20December%2018%2C%201961%2C%20Tara%20Singh%20was%20part%20of%20a%20landing%20party%20from%20INS%20Trishul%20and%20was%20directed%20to%20move%20to%20the%20island%20by%20a%20motorboat.%20On%20the%20way%2C%20his%20party%20came%20under%20fire%20from%20the%20enemy%20and%20a%20bullet%20hit%20him%20in%20the%20head%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20injury%20sustained%20during%20the%20operation%20was%20declared%20%E2%80%98head%20injury%20fracture%20skull%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20piece%20of%20bullet%20still%20remains%20lodged%20in%20his%20head.%20After%20being%20hit%2C%20he%20was%20evacuated%20and%20admitted%20to%20INS%20Ashwani%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20Arun%20Singla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Dharam%20Chand%20Chaudhary%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6it%20is%20desirable%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20instructions%20dated%20January%2031%2C%202001%2C%20which%20provided%20as%20to%20what%20type%20of%20injury%2Fcasualty%20has%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20battle%20casualty%2Finjury.%20Casualties%2Fdisabilities%20amongst%20others%20caused%20in%20an%20operation%20especially%20notified%20by%20the%20government%20from%20time%20to%20time%20have%20been%20categorised%20as%20war%20casualties%20in%20this%20document.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bench%20added%20the%20case%20of%20Tara%20Singh%20was%20covered%20under%20instructions%20dated%20January%2031%2C%202001%2C%20as%20the%20Goa%20Liberation%20Operation%20was%20notified%20by%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20applicant%20as%20such%20is%20definitely%20entitled%20to%20the%20grant%20of%20war%20injury%20pension%20and%20the%20denial%20thereof%20is%20not%20only%20illegal%2C%20arbitrary%2C%20and%20an%20abuse%20of%20power%20vested%20in%20the%20respondents%2C%20but%20also%20capricious%2C%E2%80%9D%20noted%20the%20Bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690271414000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125550%2FHELO-OPERATIONS-ON-INS-TRISHUL.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F83-year-old-navy-sailor-shot-during-goa-liberation-to-finally-get-war-pension%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bullet%20that%20struck%20Tara%20Singh%20is%20still%20embedded%20in%20his%20head.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F83-year-old-navy-sailor-shot-during-goa-liberation-to-finally-get-war-pension%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Desi%20'Oppenheimers'%20And%20How%20They%20Were%20Treated%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Hollywood%20movie%20Oppenheimer%20is%20a%20biopic%20of%20the%20scientist%20who%20made%20the%20atom%20bomb%20for%20America%2C%20but%20who%20made%20India's%20atom%20bombs%3F%20On%20the%2025th%20year%20of%20India%20becoming%20a%20nuclear%20weapons%20state%2C%20let%20us%20revisit%20the%20hard%20work%20and%20sacrifices%20of%20those%20Indian%20nuclear%20heroes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hollywood%20film%20Oppenheimer%20depicts%20the%20reality%20of%20how%20Dr%20J.%20Robert%20Oppenheimer%2C%20the%20man%20who%20is%20credited%20with%20being%20the%20'Father%20of%20the%20Atomic%20Bomb'%2C%20made%20the%20nuclear%20bomb%20for%20the%20US%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Manhattan%20Project.%20Later%2C%20his%20own%20government%20classed%20him%20as%20a%20'communist'%2C%20which%2C%20to%20Americans%2C%20almost%20meant%20being%20a%20traitor.%20He%20was%20put%20through%20a%20wringer%20of%20a%20trial%20and%20his%20security%20clearances%20were%20withdrawn%3B%20from%20being%20an%20influential%20political%20voice%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20was%20reduced%20to%20being%20almost%20an%20outcaste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%201945%20Trinity%20atomic%20test%2C%20Oppenheimer%2C%20having%20read%20Sanskrit%2C%20quoted%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20as%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20I%20become%20Death%20destroyer%20of%20the%20worlds%26quot%3B.%20His%20own%20country%20destroyed%20his%20reputation%20in%20his%20lifetime.%20Other%20countries%20like%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20also%20heaped%20humiliation%20on%20their%20atomic%20bomb-makers.%20Pakistan%20jailed%20AQ%20Khan%20for%20five%20years%20for%20running%20what%20was%20described%20as%20the%20'nuclear%20Walmart%20of%20the%20world'.%20Qian%20Sanqiang%2C%20a%20Chinese%20nuclear%20physicist%2C%20was%20deported%20to%20the%20Chinese%20countryside%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Cultural%20Revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20respects%20the%20%26quot%3BSwadeshi%20Oppenheimers%26quot%3B%20who%20made%20the%20country%20proud.%20Leading%20the%20pack%20is%20Homi%20J%20Bhabha%2C%20the%20father%20of%20India's%20atomic%20energy%20program.%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20mentions%20that%20there%20is%20now%20evidence%20that%20Oppenheimer%20was%20offered%20Indian%20repatriation%20when%20he%20was%20going%20through%20his%20ordeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-five%20years%20ago%2C%20India%20carried%20out%20five%20underground%20nuclear%20explosions%20at%20Pokharan%20in%201998%20and%20declared%20itself%20a%20'nuclear%20weapons%20state'.%20While%20about%20100%20scientists%20and%20engineers%20were%20involved%20but%20the%20most%20prominent%20were%2C%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20then%20head%20of%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%3B%20R%20Chidambaram%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%3B%20Anil%20Kakodkar%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20Bhabha%20Atomic%20Research%20Center%20(BARC)%20Mumbai%3B%20and%20K%20Santhanam%20also%20of%20DRDO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20even%20elevated%20those%20leading%20the%20country's%20efforts%20to%20become%20an%20atomic%20weapons%20state.%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20an%20aerospace%20engineer%20considered%20the%20'guiding%20force'%20for%20India's%20atom%20bombs%2C%20later%20endeared%20himself%20to%20billion-plus%20Indians%20in%20his%20avatar%20as%20the%20eleventh%20President%20of%20India.%20Also%20called%20the%20'Missile%20Man%20of%20India'%2C%20he%20famously%20dubbed%20the%20atom%20bombs%20as%20'weapons%20of%20peace'%20and%20asserted%20they%20were%20the%20currency%20to%20global%20power.%20What%20a%20crowning%20glory%20for%20the%20man%20who%20led%20Team%20Pokharan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ER%20Chidambaram%2C%20a%20physicist%20considered%20the%20chief%20designer%20of%20the%20bombs%2C%20headed%20India's%20vast%20atomic%20energy%20establishment%2C%20and%20later%20became%20the%20Principal%20Scientific%20Advisor%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20A%20shy%20person%20of%20few%20words%2C%20who%20shuns%20the%20limelight%2C%20he%20effectively%20warded%20off%20the%20criticism%20of%20India%20after%20the%20nuclear%20explosions.%20As%20a%20young%20man%20he%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20the%201974%20'peaceful%20nuclear%20explosion'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Kakodkar%2C%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%20dubbed%20'the%20perfectionist'%2C%20was%20Director%20of%20the%20Bhabha%20Atomic%20Research%20Center%20(BARC)%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20India's%20main%20nuclear%20weapons%20laboratory.%20He%20was%20responsible%20for%20all%20the%20radioactive%20components%20of%20the%20atom%20bombs.%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20secret%20testing%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20father%20and%20had%20to%20rush%20home%20for%20the%20funeral.%20After%20the%20grim%20task%2C%20he%20went%20back%20to%20create%20India's%20largest%20explosions%20ever%2C%20that%20reverberated%20across%20the%20globe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20became%20the%20chairman%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%20and%20was%20the%20brain%20behind%20the%20landmark%20Indo-US%20Civilian%20Nuclear%20Deal%20that%20ended%20the%20pariah%20status%20of%20India's%20strategic%20sector.%20Incidentally%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20offered%20to%20nominate%20him%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20which%20he%20politely%20refused%20-%20not%20unusual%20for%20a%20man%20who%20embodied%20'simple%20living%20and%20high%20thinking'.%20He%20was%20also%20involved%20as%20very%20young%20engineer%20in%20the%201974%20'Buddha%20Smiles'%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Santhanam%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Blacksmith'%2C%20the%20big%20logistics%20person%20who%20tied%20the%20teams%20together%20during%20the%201998%20atomic%20explosions.%20He%20was%20elevated%20as%20director%20of%20the%20now%20renamed%20Manohar%20Parrikar%20Institute%20for%20Defence%20Studies%20and%20Analysis%2C%20Delhi.%20He%20later%20became%20a%20critic%20of%20the%20Pokharan%20tests%20and%20questioned%20the%20yield%20of%20the%20Hydrogen%20Bomb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20heroes%20from%20the%201974%20atomic%20blasts%20like%20Homi%20J%20Sethna%2C%20the%20then%20chairman%20of%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%3B%20Raja%20Ramanna%2C%20considered%20the%20true%20'janak'%20of%20the%20atom%20bombs%2C%20who%20became%20a%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20the%20Union%20Council%20of%20Ministers.%20PK%20Iyengar%20was%20a%20key%20brain%20behind%20the%201974%20atomic%20explosion%20who%20later%20became%20chairman%20of%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission.%20All%20recognized%20as%20worthy%20sons%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20successful%20'Shakti'%20series%20of%20tests%2C%20India%20awarded%20high%20civilian%20honours%20with%20different%20Padma%20awards%20to%20four%20members%20of%20the%20atomic%20energy%20team.%20Two%20from%20the%20DRDO%20team%20were%20also%20honoured%20with%20Padma%20awards.%20Dr%20Kalam%20was%20awarded%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20of%20India%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20in%201997.%20India%20has%20a%20history%20of%20acknowledging%20the%20scientific%20heroes%20who%20made%20India%20a%20nuclear%20weapons%20state.%20A%20Bollywood%20movie%2C%20'Parmanu'%2C%20showcases%20the%20tense%20moments%20the%20scientists%20went%20through%20and%20how%20the%20satellites%20used%20by%20the%20American%20spy%20agency%20to%20snoop%20on%20Pokharan%20were%20hoodwinked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Robert%20Oppenheimer%20was%20hounded%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJairam%20Ramesh%2C%20a%20technocrat%20and%20MP%2C%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3BRobert%20Oppenheimer%20is%20credited%20with%20being%20the%20father%20of%20the%20atomic%20bomb.%20When%20he%20witnessed%20the%20first%20nuclear%20explosion%20in%20the%20deserts%20of%20New%20Mexico%20in%20the%20US%20on%20July%2016%2C%201945%2C%20by%20his%20own%20admission%20he%20immediately%20thought%20of%20a%20verse%20from%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20-%20'Now%20I%20become%20Death%2C%20the%20destroyer%20of%20worlds'.%20This%20is%20a%20reference%20to%20Chapter%2011%2C%20Verse%2032.%20Virtually%20all%20translations%20of%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BKaala%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20verse%20render%20it%20as%20%26quot%3BTime%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bthe%20eternal%20Time-Spirit%26quot%3B.%20But%20Oppenheimer%20used%20%26quot%3BKaala%26quot%3B%20to%20mean%20%26quot%3BDeath%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20because%20he%20had%20studied%20Sanskrit%20in%20the%20early%201930s%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%20at%20Berkeley%20under%20Arthur%20Ryder%20whose%20translation%20of%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20had%20appeared%20in%201929.%20It%20was%20Ryder%20who%20had%20translated%20Kaala%20as%20Death%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20revelation%2C%20%C2%A0Jairam%20Ramesh%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIncidentally%2C%20Bakhtiar%20Dadabhoy%2C%20in%20his%20recent%202023%20biography%20of%20Homi%20J.%20Bhabha%20writes%20that%20when%20Oppenheimer%20was%20under%20attack%20in%20the%20early%201950s%20for%20his%20communist%20leanings%2C%20Bhabha%2C%20after%20consulting%20Nehru%2C%20sounded%20him%20out%20on%20immigrating%20to%20India.%20There%20is%20really%20no%20conclusive%20archival%20evidence%20for%20this%2C%20but%20Bhabha%20may%20well%20have%20verbally%20sounded%20Oppenheimer%20out.%20But%20ironically%2C%20Bernard%20Peters%2C%20who%20was%20betrayed%20as%20a%20communist%20by%20Oppenheimer%20to%20the%20American%20authorities%20in%201949%2C%20was%20invited%20by%20Bhabha%20to%20the%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Fundamental%20Research%20(TIFR)%2C%20Mumbai%20in%201951.%20Peters%20made%20very%20important%20scientific%20contributions%20in%20cosmic%20rays%20and%20nuclear%20research%20at%20TIFR%20before%20immigrating%20to%20Denmark.%20He%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%20in%201985%26quot%3B.%20Such%20are%20the%20palace%20intrigues%20that%20played%20out%20in%20the%20nuclear%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Pallava%20Bagla%20is%20a%20New%20Delhi-based%20science%20communicator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690271400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fd8iu8md_robert-oppenheimer-afp-file-1200_625x300_21_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-desi-oppenheimers-and-how-they-were-treated-in-india-4239054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hollywood%20movie%20Oppenheimer%20is%20a%20biopic%20of%20the%20scientist%20who%20made%20the%20atom%20bomb%20for%20America%2C%20but%20who%20made%20India's%20atom%20bombs%3FLet%20us%20revisit%20the%20hard%20work%20and%20sacrifices%20of%20those%20Indian%20nuclear%20heroes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-desi-oppenheimers-and-how-they-were-treated-in-india-4239054%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-desi-oppenheimers-and-how-they-were-treated-in-india-4239054%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-desi-oppenheimers-and-how-they-were-treated-in-india-4239054%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Class%201%20girl%20raped%20in%20school%20hostel%20in%20Chhattisgarh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690270954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102101639%2Cimgsize-35662.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2Fclass-1-girl-raped-in-school-hostel-in-chhattisgarhs-sukma-district%2Farticleshow%2F102101640.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20unidentified%20man%20allegedly%20raped%20a%20minor%20girl%20in%20the%20hostel%20of%20a%20residential%20school%20in%20Sukma%20district%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20an%20official%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2Fclass-1-girl-raped-in-school-hostel-in-chhattisgarhs-sukma-district%2Farticleshow%2F102101640.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22North%20Korea%20Fires%20Twin%20Ballistic%20Missiles%20After%20US%20Nuclear-Powered%20Submarine%C2%A0Arrives%20in%20South%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%