3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20the%20arguments%20of%20which%20he%20has%20taken%20considerably%20further%20in%20this%20interview%2C%20Guha%20said%20Modi%20would%20show%20%E2%80%9Cmoral%20growth%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Credeem%20himself%E2%80%9D%20and%20also%20provide%20%E2%80%9Csome%20sense%20of%20atonement%E2%80%9D%20for%20his%20failure%20to%20contain%20the%20riots%20of%202002%2C%20when%20he%20was%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20if%20now%20he%20would%20sack%20Biren%20Singh%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20address%20parliament%2C%20Guha%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CHe%E2%80%99s%20being%20shielded%20by%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%A6they%20want%20to%20protect%20him%2C%20placate%20him%20and%20flatter%20him%20and%20not%20expose%20him%20to%20debate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20connection%2C%20Guha%20also%20said%20%E2%80%9COm%20Birla%20and%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%E2%80%99s%20partisan%20conduct%20is%20shocking%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuha%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20act%2C%20both%20at%20the%20state%20and%20central%20level%2C%20has%20damaged%20the%20Indian%20Republic%20and%20Indian%20democracy%20and%20the%20prospects%20of%20our%20country%20and%20its%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuha%20said%20Manipur%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20mixture%20of%20anarchy%20and%20civil%20war%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20speaks%20about%20how%20Manipur%20is%20different%20to%20earlier%20inter-communal%20conflicts%20in%20other%20states.%20He%20has%20two%20reasons%20for%20saying%20so.%20He%20also%20compares%20and%20contrasts%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20today%20with%20what%20happened%20in%20Gujarat%20in%202002.%20He%20also%20analyses%20why%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20still%20in%20office%20and%20provides%20three%20separate%2