20to%20dramatic%20scenes%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20triggered%20a%20heated%20exchange%20between%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20and%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20and%20emerged%20as%20a%20the%20biggest%20suspense%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%20Singh%20Gudha%2C%20MLA%20from%20Udaipurwati%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Jhunjhunu%20district%2C%20walked%20into%20the%20Assembly%20yesterday%20and%20started%20waving%20a%20red%20diary%20that%20he%20claimed%20could%20%26quot%3Bexpose%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot.%20The%20MLA%20was%20then%20marshalled%20out%20of%20the%20House.%20He%20has%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20assaulted%20and%20that%20some%20Congress%20leaders%20snatched%20the%20diary%20from%20his%20hand%20and%20tore%20some%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dramatic%20Assembly%20episode%20followed%20Mr%20Gudha's%20sudden%20dismissal%20as%20a%20minister%20following%20his%20remarks%20on%20the%20state%20government's%20%26quot%3Bfailure%26quot%3B%20to%20prevent%20crimes%20against%20women.%20Amid%20the%20uproar%20in%20the%20House%20over%20the%20horrifying%20video%20of%20two%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20MLA%20said%20Friday%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20true%20and%20should%20be%20accepted%20that%20we%20have%20failed%20in%20women's%20safety.%20Instead%20of%20Manipur%2C%20we%20should%20look%20within%20ourselves%20why%20atrocities%20on%20women%20have%20increased%20in%20Rajasthan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-time%20MLA%20is%20now%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20row%20over%20the%20red%20diary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERed%20Diary%3A%20Claims%20And%20Counters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gudha%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20diary%20contains%20explosive%20information%20about%20Chief%20Minister%20Gehlot.%20The%20diary%2C%20he%20says%2C%20belongs%20to%20Dharmendra%20Rathore%2C%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Rajasthan%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation.%20Mr%20Gudha%20has%20claimed%20this%20diary%20contains%20details%20of%20pay-offs%20made%20by%20the%20Gehlot%20camp%20to%20MLAs%2C%20Independents%20and%20others%20to%20save%20his%20government%20during%20the%202020%20rebellion%20led%20by%20Sachin%20Pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diary%20also%20contains%20details%20of%20payoffs%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20ensure%20the%20victory%20of%20its%20candidates%20despite%20a%20tough%20contest%20from%20BJP-backed%20Independent%20and%20media%20baron%20Subhash%20Chandra%2C%20Mr%20Gudha%20has%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20MLA%20has%20said%20this%20diary%20was%20in%20Mr%20Rathore's%20home%20when%20Income%20Tax%20officials%20conducted%20a%20raid.%20Mr%20Gudha%20said%20he%20managed%20to%20retrieve%20the%20red%20diary%20before%20tax%20officials%20found%20it%2C%20allegedly%20on%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20request.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20he%20has%20said%2C%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20burn%20the%20diary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20trashed%20Mr%20Gudha's%20claims%2C%20calling%20them%20fabricated.%20Senior%20party%20leader%20and%20minister%20for%20parliamentary%20affairs%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20has%20said%20the%20MLA%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20hatched%20this%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Opportunity%20For%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspense%20surrounding%20the%20red%20diary%20has%20provided%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20with%20a%20political%20weapon%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Assembly%20polls.%20The%20ruling%20Congress%20has%20been%20trying%20hard%20to%20ensure%20that%20its%20infighting%20does%20not%20undo%20its%20poll%20prospects.%20A%20corruption%20scandal%20at%20this%20point%2C%20in%20which%20none%20other%20than%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20been%20accused%2C%20can%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20big%20blow%20to%20the%20state%20government's%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20and%20Rajasthan's%20key%20BJP%20leader%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20acc