%20IRCTC%20site%20and%20App.%20Technical%20team%20of%20CRIS%20is%20resolving%20the%20issue.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAlternatively%20tickets%20can%20be%20booked%20through%20other%20B2C%20players%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Makemytrip%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20IRCTC%20(%40IRCTCofficial)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIRCTCofficial%2Fstatus%2F1683706786522750980%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20people%20who%20want%20to%20book%20ticket%20can%20visit%20the%20PRS%20counter%20or%20contact%20web%20services%20agents%20like%20Make%20My%20Trip%2C%20Amazon%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20users%20started%20complaining%20to%20IRCTC%20claiming%20that%20their%20money%20has%20been%20deducted%20and%20sought%20to%20know%20when%20they%20will%20get%20it%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20they%20tried%20to%20book%20tickets%20through%20the%20partner%20services%20but%20were%20unable%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20IRCTC%20website%2C%20the%20PSU%20was%20incorporated%20as%20an%20extended%20arm%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20to%20upgrade%2C%20professionalize%20and%20manage%20the%20catering%20and%20hospitality%20services%20at%20stations%2C%20on%20trains%20and%20other%20locations%20and%20to%20promote%20domestic%20and%20international%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PSU%20has%20five%20zonal%20Offices%20at%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Chennai%20and%20Secunderabad%20and%2010%20regional%20offices%20at%20Lucknow%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20Ahmadabad%2C%20Guwahati%2C%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20Patna%2C%20Ernakulam%20and%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIRCTC%20also%20offers%20budget%20hotels%2C%20special%20tour%20packages%2C%20and%20information%20for%20travellers%20on%20its%20website%20and%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690268640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2