alluvar'%20Portraits%20Dictum%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2FMadras_High_Court_PTI.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20facing%20stiff%20opposition%20to%20its%20decision%20to%20disallow%20statues%20and%20portraits%20of%20anyone%20other%20than%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Thiruvalluvar%20to%20be%20displayed%20anywhere%20inside%20court%20premises%20across%20the%20state%20and%20in%20Puducherry%2C%20the%20Madras%20high%20court%20has%20assured%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20that%20status%20quo%20can%20be%20maintained%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20portraits%20of%20the%20likes%20of%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20others%20need%20not%20be%20removed%20from%20court%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fmadras-high-court%2Fmadras-high-court-circular-only-portraits-statues-of-mahatma-gandhi-and-saint-thiruvalluvar-permitted-inside-court-premises-233373%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20registrar%20general%20of%20the%20court%20noted%20in%20the%20July%207%20circular%20that%20the%20court%20had%20on%20April%2011%20considered%20a%20similar%20request%2C%20and%20turned%20it%20down.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20the%20high%20court%20had%20received%20representations%20from%20the%20Advocates%E2%80%99%20Association%20and%20other%20associations%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20seeking%20permission%20to%20display%20portraits%20of%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20directed%20principal%20district%20judges%2C%20district%20judges%2C%20principal%20judges%2C%20district%20judge-cum-chief%20judicial%20magistrate%20of%20the%20districts%20and%20the%20chief%20judge%20of%20Puducherry%2C%20to%20adhere%20to%20this%20dictum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20said%20that%20in%20several%20hearings%20which%20started%20in%202008%2C%20the%20court%20had%20considered%20requests%20to%20put%20up%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20and%20other%20national%20leaders%E2%80%99%20portraits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%20and%202011%2C%20the%20court%20had%20held%20that%20because%20the%20damage%20of%20such%20statues%20could%20lead%20to%20friction%20and%20also%20because%20there%20were%20demands%20to%20erect%20politicians%E2%80%99%20statues%2C%20there%20could%20not%20be%20any%20more%20status%20or%20portraits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%20and%202018%2C%20these%20resolutions%20were%20once%20again%20upheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Fmadras-hc-status-quo-on-removal-of-br-ambedkar-portraits-from-courts%2Farticleshow%2F102092781.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20Monday%2C%20July%2024%2C%20the%20department%20of%20information%20and%20public%20relations%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20Chief%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Vijaykumar%20Gangapurwala%20told%20Tamil%20Nadu%20law%20minister%20S.%20Ragupathy%20that%20no%20order%20had%20been%20passed%20to%20remove%20portraits%20of%20any%20leader%20from%20the%20court%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fmadras-hc-chief-justice-must-intervene-to-allow-ambedkars-portraits-in-courts-says-annamalai%2Farticle67116660.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20president%20K.%20Annamalai%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2024%2C%20appealed%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Madras%20HC%20to%20intervene%20and%20permit%20the%20display%20of%20portraits%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20in%20courts%20and%20their%20premises%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnamalai%20called%20the%20decision%20disappointing%20and%20sought%20to%20remind%20the%20court%20that%20Ambedkar%20was%20the