w%20one%20starting%20at%20the%20company.%20This%20is%20a%20move%20that%20is%20part%20of%20the%20world's%20richest%20man's%20fascination%20with%20the%20letter%20X.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20continuation%20of%20the%20steps%20he%20has%20taken%20to%20realise%20this%20dream.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20his%20other%20company%20Tesla%20rolled%20out%20cars%20to%20complete%20the%20'SEXY-%20line-up.%20However%2C%20the%20renaming%20of%20its%20entry%20level%20sedan%20from%20Model%20E%20to%203%20changed%20it%20to%20%26quot%3BS3XY%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20per%20Mr%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20several%20tweets%20going%20viral%20after%20Twitter's%20renaming%2C%20the%20X%20identity%20was%20born%20when%20he%20launched%20an%20online%20banking%20services%20platform%20called%20X.com%20that%20later%20became%20part%20of%20PayPal.%20Mr%20Musk%20walked%20away%20with%20%24165%20million%2C%20and%20the%20dream%20to%20create%20a%20bigger%20X%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20obsession%20led%20him%20to%20establish%20Space%20Exploration%20Technologies%20Corporation%2C%20also%20known%20as%20SpaceX.%20As%20per%20claims%20made%20by%20several%20social%20media%20users%2C%20the%20X%20in%20the%20name%20symbolised%20a%20rocket's%20trajectory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20envisioned%20a%20car%20line-up%20with%20model%20names%20that%20spelled%20out%20%26quot%3BSEXY%26quot%3B.%20So%2C%20Tesla%2C%20the%20electric%20car%20manufacturer%20owned%20by%20Mr%20Musk%2C%20started%20launching%20Model%20S%20and%20later%20on%2C%20Model%20X%20and%20Y.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ford%20had%20already%20acquired%20the%20rights%20to%20Model%20E%2C%20which%20sounded%20Henry%20Ford's%20iconic%20Model%20T%2C%20as%20per%20an%20old%20%3Cem%3EUSA%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20told%20the%20US%20outlet%20that%20in%202010%20Tesla%20had%20signed%20a%20contract%20in%20which%2C%20%26quot%3Bamong%20other%20things%2C%20Tesla%20agreed%20not%20to%20register%20or%20use%20Model%20E.%20When%20Tesla%20later%20sought%20to%20register%20the%20Model%20E%20trademark%2C%20Ford%20insisted%20that%20Tesla%20abide%20by%20the%20parties'%20earlier%20agreement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20car%20launched%20in%20the%20US%20in%20July%2C%202017%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BModel%203%20was%20going%20to%20be%20called%20Model%20E%2C%20for%20obvious%20dumb%20humor%20reasons%2C%20but%20Ford%20sued%20to%20block%20it%2C%20so%20now%20it%20is%20S3X.%20Totally%20different%20%3A)%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20all%20four%20models%20have%20been%20launched%20(the%20last%20to%20launch%20was%20Model%20Y%20in%202020)%2C%20there%20is%20speculation%20that%20Tesla%20will%20drop%20the%20'Model'%20plus%20'letter'%20naming%20scheme%20to%20complete%20the%20'S3XY'%20line-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690266660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Flesbcfj8_elon-musk-with-model-y-afp-1200_625x300_25_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-twitter-is-named-x-a-look-at-elon-musks-s3xy-naming-strategy-for-cars-4238936%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20several%20tweets%20going%20viral%20after%20Twitter's%20renaming%2C%20the%20X%20identity%20was%20born%20when%20he%20launched%20an%20online%20banking%20services%20platform.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-twitter-is-named-x-a-look-at-elon-musks-s3xy-naming-strategy-for-cars-4238936%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-twitter-is-named-x-a-look-at-elon-musks-s3xy-naming-strategy-for-cars-4238936%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-twitter-is-named-x-a-look-at-elon-musks-s3xy-naming-strategy-for-cars-4238936%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Byju's%20'regularly%20disregarded'%20former%20director's%20advice%2C%20says%20Prosus