ings%20of%20the%20drawn%20second%20Test%20here%2C%20as%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20was%20to%20score%20quickly%20and%20set%20an%20imposing%20target%20for%20the%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20scoring%20at%207.54%20runs%20per%20over%20on%20day%204%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20(they%20declared%20at%20181%2F2%20in%2024%20overs)%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20experts%20who%20asked%20Ishan%20during%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%20if%20this%20is%20the%20way%20India%20would%20play%20Tests%20matches%20in%20future%2C%20much%20like%20England%2C%20whose%20aggressive%20style%20of%20playing%20has%20been%20give%20the%20term%20'Bazball'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20necessary%20that%20everyday%20you%20come%20in%20and%20start%20playing%20fast%20cricket.%20That%20should%20depend%20on%20the%20situation.%20The%20condition%20of%20the%20pitches%20also%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20how%20quickly%20one%20can%20score%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kishan%2C%20who%20was%20promoted%20in%20the%20batting%20order%20to%20score%20quick%20runs%20on%20the%20fourth%20day%20of%20the%20second%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20scored%20a%2034-ball%2052%20to%20help%20India%20set%20a%20365-run%20victory%20target%20for%20the%20West%20Indies%20but%20rain%20played%20spoilsport%20on%20the%20fifth%20and%20final%20day%20on%20Sunday%20to%20deny%20India%20a%20clean%20sweep%20of%20the%20two-match%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMostly%2C%20where%20we%20play%2C%20wickets%20are%20not%20that%20easy...there%20is%20turn%20and%20bounce.%20So%2C%20playing%20quick%20on%20those%20surface%20there%20is%20no%20point%20because%20you%20need%20to%20read%20the%20wicket%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20get%20a%20wicket%20where%20you%20can%20score%20quick%20runs%20and%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20to%20do%20that%2C%20then%20every%20player%20in%20the%20(Indian)%20team%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20perform%20that%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20kind%20of%20players%20we%20have%20and%20the%20number%20of%20formats%20and%20matches%20that%20we%20play%2C%20everyone%20knows%20his%20role%20--%20which%20match%20one%20has%20to%20play%20in%20what%20manner.%20So%2C%20personally%2C%20I%20feel%2C%20every%20match%20we%20don't%20need%20to%20play%20like%20that%20(score%20quickly)%2C%20but%20it%20should%20be%20situation-based.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20journey%20of%20patience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan's%20journey%20has%20been%20one%20of%20patience%20and%20endurance%2C%20where%20he%20has%20had%20to%20bide%20his%20time%20and%20wait%20for%20opportunities%20to%20come%20his%20way%20in%20all%20three%20formats%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20he%20dealt%20with%20the%20waiting%20game%20and%20whether%20it%20was%20frustrating%20to%20be%20sitting%20out%20and%20dealing%20with%20disappointments%2C%20the%20young%20cricketer%20said%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20every%20individual%20is%20different%20.%20It%20might%20be%20frustrating%20for%20some%2C%20but%20someone%20else%20can%20take%20it%20as%20a%20challenge...%20that%20'I%20am%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20get%20to%20that%20level'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20appreciate%20if%20someone%20else%20gets%20selected%20in%20the%20side%20and%20performs%20because%20I%20know%20how%20tough%20this%20game%20is%2C%20how%20you%20are%20tested%20mentally%2C%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20give%20that%20performance%20when%20there%20is%20so%20much%20expectation%20and%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20make%20an%20effort%20whenever%20I'm%20off%20or%20not%20playing%20that%20I%20concentrate%20on%20my%20practice%20and%20prepare%20myself%20that%20whenever%20I%20get%20the%20opportunity%2C%20I%20give%20my%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Got%20tips%20from%20Rishabh%20Pant%20at%20NCA'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20said%20that%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20the%20man%20he%20replaced%20in%20the%20India%20Test%20side%20for%20the%20tour%20of%20West%20Indies%2C%20gave%20him%20useful%20tips%20during%20his%20stay%20at%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%20is%20currently%20rehabilitating%20at%20the%20NCA%20after%20suffering%20a%20horrific%20car%20accident%20in%20December%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20knows%20me%20from%20U-19%20days...%20how%20I%20play%2C%20how%20I%20think%2C%20so%20we%20keep%20interacting.%20What%20I%20think%20he%20needs%20to%20do%20to%20improve%20I%20tell%20him%20and%20the%20same%20is%20the%20case%20with%20him.%20He%20also%20tries%20to%20help%20me%20and%20ensure%20I%20give%20it%20my%20best%20shot%20on%20a%20tour.%20And%20I%20am%20very%20thankful%20that%20he%20he%20gave%20me%20some%20good%20points%20at%20the%20NCA.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20he%20has%20done%20very%20well%20in%20Tests%2C%20and%20the%20number%20at%20which%20we%20bat...Rishabh%20bats%2C%20it%20is%20very%20important%20for%20us%20to%20understand%20the%20situation.%20If%20four%20wickets%20fall%20quickly%20and%20a%20partnership%20is%20required%20then%20we%20cannot%20play%20that%20fast-scoring%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20we%20need%20to%20keep%20the%20match%20in%20mind...%20what%20we%20need%20to%20do%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time%20because%20it%20is%20a%20five-day%20game%20and%20last%20day%20is%20very%20important.%20And%2C%20planning%20and%20execution%20is%20the%20most%20important%20aspect%20in%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERohit%20knows%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20young%20players%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20said%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20experience%20and%20how%20he%20handles%20the%20young%20players%20gives%20them%20confidence%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bcomfort%20zone%26quot%3B%20to%20play%20with%20a%20clear%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20very%20experienced%20captain.%20He%20gives%20his%20best%2C%20how%20to%20keep%20players%20in%20comfort%20zone%2C%20don't%20let%20pressure%20get%20the%20better%20of%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20when%20I%20came%20out%20to%20bat%20(in%20the%20second%20innings%20at%20Port%20of%20Spain)%2C%20he%20said%20'play%20your%20game%2C%20plan%20your%20innings%20and%20don't%20think%20who%20has%20said%20what'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20youngster%2C%20that%20is%20a%20huge%20plus%20point%20that%20the%20captain%20has%20faith%20in%20you%2C%20that%20I%20can%20handle%20the%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690266240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fv1mb79uo_ishan-kishan_625x300_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fteam-india-to-adopt-bazball-approach-in-tests-ishan-kishan-gives-blunt-response-4238804%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20scoring%20at%207.54%20runs%20per%20over%20on%20day%204%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20(they%20declared%20at%20181%2F2%20in%2024%20overs)%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20experts%20who%20asked%20Ishan%20during%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%20if%20this%20is%20the%20way%20India%20would%20play%20Tests%20matches%20in%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A347%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fteam-india-to-adopt-bazball-approach-in-tests-ishan-kishan-gives-blunt-response-4238804%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fteam-india-to-adopt-bazball-approach-in-tests-ishan-kishan-gives-blunt-response-4238804%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fteam-india-to-adopt-bazball-approach-in-tests-ishan-kishan-gives-blunt-response-4238804%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ban%20on%20autos%2C%20bikes%20on%20B'luru-Mysuru%20Eway%20from%20August%201%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690265845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%