E%20is%20having%20a%20direct%20impact%20on%20the%20IT%20industry.%20With%20existing%20projects%20stalled%2C%20and%20without%20any%20new%20projects%2C%20the%20Indian%20IT%20sector%20does%20not%20have%20the%20same%20need%20to%20recruit%20new%20engineers%20at%20the%20previous%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIT%20firms%20are%20now%20discussing%20terms%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9Cutilisation%20of%20existing%20bench%20strength%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cupskilling%E2%80%9D%20in%20their%20financial%20commentary%2C%20said%20the%20report.%20This%20points%20towards%20the%20depleted%20recruitment%20numbers.%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20IT%20leaders%20believe%20that%20the%20upcoming%20AI%20transformation%20will%20not%20adversely%20affect%20newly%20hired%20engineers%2C%20the%20data%20seems%20to%20suggest%20otherwise%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20top%20five%20IT%20firms%20are%20estimated%20to%20recruit%20less%20than%2010%25%20of%20the%20graduating%20class%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%20number%20of%20new%20engineers%20that%20this%20sector%20recruits%20normally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenowned%20companies%20such%20as%20TCS%2C%20Infosys%2C%20and%20Wipro%2C%20which%20have%20been%20popular%20choices%20among%20outgoing%20engineering%20graduates%20for%20their%20reliable%20job%20opportunities%2C%20are%20now%20signaling%20a%20less%20favourable%20job%20market%20for%20engineers%20this%20year.%20TCS%20has%20already%20postponed%20onboarding%20new%20recruits%20by%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690265402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25110639%2Fimage-1168.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ffresh-it-hiring-at-three-year-low-in-fy24-amid-looming-us-recession-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20FY22%2C%20the%20Indian%20IT%20sector%20recruited%203.9%20lakh%20new%20graduates%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20demand%20for%2