3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25105724%2FF1dfIKMXoAAY2fN.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20mob%20attacked%20the%20Meghalaya%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(CMO)%20in%20Tura%20on%20Monday%20(July%2024)%20while%20chief%20minister%20Conrad%20Sangma%20was%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20some%20local%20leaders%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Feast-and-northeast%2Fmeghalaya-cms-office-attacked-by-mob-five-security-personnel-injured-1240302.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mob%20pelted%20stones%20at%20the%20CMO%20injuring%20five%20policemen%20and%20shattering%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20windows.%20Sangma%20was%20inside%20the%20building%20when%20the%20attack%20took%20place%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20had%20invited%20local%20organisations%20who%20were%20demanding%20Tura%E2%80%99s%20designation%20as%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20winter%20capital%20and%20the%20proper%20implementation%20of%20a%2051-year-old%20job%20reservation%20policy.%20Cabinet%20ministers%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20were%20also%20present%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmob-attacks-meghalaya-chief-ministers-office-in-tura-during-a-meeting%2Farticle67116979.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mob%20of%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20people%20gathered%20outside%20the%20CMO%20about%20three%20hours%20into%20the%20meeting%20with%20the%20agitating%20groups%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmob-attacks-meghalaya-chief-ministers-office-in-tura-during-a-meeting%2Farticle67116979.ece%5C%22%3Epolice%20fired%20tear%20gas%20shells%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20disperse%20the%20mob%20after%20the%20five%20policemen%20got%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20happened%20today%20was%20very%20unfortunate.%20We%20have%20the%20entire%20video%20recording%20of%20the%20people%20who%20instigated%20%5Bthe%20violence%5D%20and%20necessary%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20according%20to%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Sangma%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20unable%20to%20understand%20how%20this%20chaos%20broke%20out.%20We%20have%20been%20organising%20a%20peaceful%20hunger%20strike%20over%20the%20last%20few%20days.%20The%20sloganeering%20and%20stone-pelting%20were%20started%20by%20anti-social%20elements%20whom%20we%20have%20never%20seen%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laben%20Ch.%20Marak%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20one%20of%20the%20organisations%2C%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangma%20later%20released%20a%20video%20message%20where%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Feast-and-northeast%2Fmeghalaya-cms-office-attacked-by-mob-five-security-personnel-injured-1240302.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20talks%20were%20almost%20over%2C%20with%20an%20agreement%20to%20meet%20in%20Shillong%20for%20further%20discussions%2C%20when%20they%20heard%20sloganeering%20outside.%20The%20NGO%20leaders%20went%20outside%20to%20calm%20the%20mob%20but%20realised%20that%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20members%20of%20their%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20discussion%20was%20almost%20over%2C%20we%20heard%20sloganeering%20from%20outside.%20I%20asked%20them%20not%20to%20create%20any%20scene%20out%20here.%20Their%20leaders%20(of%20the%20NGOs%20in%20the%20talks)%20went%20outside%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20people.%20They%20came%20back%20and%20said%20they%20did%20not%20know%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sangma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Feast-and-northeast%2Fmeghalaya-cms-office-attacked-by-mob-five-security-personnel-injured-1240302.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20unidentified%20individuals%20were%20trying%20to%20create%20some%20kind%20of%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2Feast-and-northeast%2Fmeghalaya-cms-office-attacked-by-mob-five-security-personnel-injured-1240302.html%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20those%20injured%20and%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20would%20also%20bear%20the%20treatment%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690264211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25105724%2FF1dfIKMXoAAY2fN.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmob-attacks-meghalaya-cms-office-rs-50000-assistance-to-injured-announced%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20mob%20pelted%20stones%20at%20the%20CMO%2C%20injuring%20five%20policemen%20and%20shattering%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20windows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmob-attacks-meghalaya-cms-office-rs-50000-assistance-to-injured-announced%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MP%20BJP%20MLA%20Criticises%20Bulldozer%20Action%20Against%20'His%20Aide'%20Who%20Urinated%20on%20Tribal%20Man%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25110427%2F325401394_578162986994761_5237737778166316852_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MLA%20Kedarnath%20Shukla%20has%20criticised%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20police%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20bulldoze%20the%20house%20of%20Pravesh%20Shukla%2C%20who%20has%20been%20jailed%20for%20urinating%20on%20an%20Adivasi%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20house%20was%20their%20(Pravesh%E2%80%99s%20family%E2%80%99s)%20ancestral%20property.%20It%20was%20their%20family%20home%20from%20their%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20time.%20It%20should%20not%20have%20been%20demolished%20by%20the%20authorities%E2%80%A6%20No%20matter%20who%20is%20the%20accused%2C%20his%20family%20should%20not%20be%20made%20to%20suffer%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kedarnath%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fkedarnath-shukla-dashmant-rawat-shivraj-singh-chouhan-8857685%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20statement%20gains%20significance%20also%20because%20the%20Congress%20had%20been%20alleging%20that%20Pravesh%20was%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20particular%20to%20Sidhi%20MLA%20Kedarnath.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20name%20of%20the%20accused%20is%20being%20told%20as%20Pravesh%20Shukla%2C%20who%20is%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20BJP%20MLA.%20The%20MLA%20is%20Kedar%20Nath%20Shukla.%20There%20are%20photographs%20of%20the%20accused%20urinating%20on%20the%20tribal%20youth%20along%20with%20veteran%20BJP%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmp-man-urinate-tribal-youth-viral-video%5C%22%3EAbbas%20Hafeez%20had%20tweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20soon%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20after%20a%20video%20of%20the%20urination%20incident%20went%20viral%2C%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20met%20the%20victim%20and%20washed%20his%20feet.%20The%20police%20invoked%20the%20stringent%20National%20Security%20Act%20and%20arrested%20the%20accused%2C%20and%20demolished%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20portions%20of%20Pravesh%E2%80%99s%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20up%20for%20Pravesh%2C%20Kedarnath%20claimed%20he%20was%20not%20disagreeing%20with%20the%20BJP.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CMy%20party%20speaks%20for%20justice.%20As%20humans%2C%20it%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20think%20and%20apply%20our%20minds%E2%80%A6%20and%20not%