dd%20bio-fertilisers%20within%20the%20first%20month%20of%20the%20sowing%20period%20for%20a%20better%20yield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20bio-fertilisers%2C%20less%20dosage%20of%20bio-pesticides%20and%20bio-fungicides%20is%20used.%20As%20microorganisms%20keep%20multiplying%2C%20you%20do%20not%20have%20to%20spray%20multiple%20times.%20This%20reduces%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20input%20costs%20by%20one-third%20and%20prevents%20them%20from%20compounding%20debts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sangita%20has%20helped%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20farmers%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Punjab%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsangita-swalakhe-4-1689772226-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324368%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Sangita%20has%20helped%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20farmers%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Punjab%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20some%20limitations%20associated%20with%20bio%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20alternatives%20cannot%20be%20used%20simultaneously%20with%20chemicals%20or%20in%20temperatures%20exceeding%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20open%20fields%2C%20as%20it%20would%20harm%20microorganisms.%20Microorganisms%20can%20tolerate%20temperatures%20up%20to%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%20require%20a%20humid%20environment%20with%20shade%20to%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Sangita%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20these%20bio%20alternatives%20has%20increased%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20are%20diverting%20towards%20bio%20alternatives%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321571%2Famith-kishan-quits-job-to-start-hebbuvu-organic-and-natural-farming-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20I%20introduced%20farmers%20to%20these%20products%2C%20they%20could%20not%20believe%20that%20these%20can%20replace%20chemical%20fertilisers.%20But%20today%2C%20we%20have%20so%20many%20farmers%20who%20find%20my%20products%20useful.%20These%20bio%20alternatives%20will%20bring%20a%20revolution%20in%20the%20farming%20sector%2C%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20contribute%20to%20that%20is%20extremely%20satisfying%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20her%20work%2C%20Sangita%20has%20been%20felicitated%20with%20many%20awards%20including%20the%20Honour%20of%20Excellence%20award%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%20in%202018%20and%20the%20Maharashtra%20Udyogini%20Puraskar%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20picture%20credits%3A%20Sangita%20Sawalakhe%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5