ing%20building%20is%20a%20routine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20duty%20call%20for%2024%20hours%2C%20it%20is%20the%20passion%20for%20wildlife%20that%20keeps%20the%20veterinarian%20going.%20She%20has%20been%20in%20rescue%20missions%20which%20entail%20risks%20for%20both%20her%20and%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20on%20a%20mission%2C%20the%20animal%20is%20always%20my%20top%20priority.%20Leopards%20are%20frequently%20the%20ones%20we%20rescue%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20they%20are%20just%20as%20afraid%20of%20us%20as%20we%20are%20of%20them.%20There%20are%20significant%20risks%20of%20injury%20for%20both%20myself%20and%20the%20animal%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeghana%20adds%20that%20when%20she%20is%20on%20a%20rescue%20mission%2C%20she%20does%20not%20even%20think%20for%20a%20second%20before%20risking%20her%20life%20to%20save%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Dinesh%20Kumar%20Y%20K%2C%20the%20deputy%20conservator%20of%20forests%20(DCF)%20of%20Mangaluru%20division%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20on%20several%20missions%20with%20Meghana%20says%20the%20same.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20very%20light-footed%20and%20quick-witted%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20her%20work.%20She%20does%20not%20even%20blink%20before%20jumping%20into%20wells%20and%20climbing%20floors%20of%20buildings%20to%20save%20the%20animal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meghana%20had%20to%20jump%20in%20a%2020%20feet%20well%20to%20rescue%20a%20leopardess%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwildlife-vet-2-1689226028.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F0