C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mission%20is%20not%20to%20earn%20from%20a%20commercial%20set%20up%2C%20but%20to%20spread%20awareness%20on%20the%20history%20of%20Awadh%2C%20its%20last%20King%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah%2C%20freedom%20fighter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F156185%2Fbegum-hazrat-mahal-british-1857-mutiny%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBegum%20Hazrat%20Mahal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20our%20family%20history.%20For%20this%2C%20I%20get%20immense%20love%2C%20honour%2C%20and%20respect%2C%20which%20is%20priceless.%20That%20is%20my%20real%20earning%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689227864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D323582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20descendant%20of%20King%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah%20and%20Begum%20Hazrat%20Mahal%2C%20Manzilat%20runs%20a%20home%20diner%20that%20keeps%20a%20number%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20Kolkata%20Biryani%2C%20which%20she%20says%20has%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20region%20of%20Lucknow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323582%2Fmanzilat-descendant-of-wajid-ali-shah-keeps-family-history-of-kolkata-biryani-alive%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2219-YO%20Self-Taught%20Chocolatier%20Preserves%20India%E2%80%99s%20Indigenous%20Fruits%2C%20Earns%20Rs%201%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndoor%20games%2C%20work%20from%20home%2C%20online%20classes%2C%20Dalgona%20coffee%2C%20exploring%20your%20inner%20baker%E2%80%A6sounds%20familiar%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20when%